------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lesson 27 语法讲解

+ in        在...里面
+ on        在...上面

There is a book in my bag.
There is a book on the table.
There is a man on the tree.

on the tree         长在树上
in the tree         在树上

Hi is on the plane / train / ship

There is a picture on the wall.
There is a window in the wall.
There is a door in the wall.

